column5: Hi guys My girlfriend and I are hoping to head up to the Ramsey area on wednesday and are looking for any information on where to tent for free. We only have a 12' aluminum with a 4.5 so we dont want to be too far away from decent fishing as well. It doesnt have to be Ramsey, we are just looking for somewhere not too far from sudbury that we can spend a nice evening and catch some fish. thanks
It is all crown land as I understand it, just motor down the lake and find a likely spot. I did it last year.
It's not a huge secret per say, but still, specifics on this area would best be relegated to pm's.
